        <h3>Digital PCR</h3>
        <p class="method-desc">Goes beyond detection to tell you exactly how much of a target marker is present. Precision counting at the molecular level for products where the detail matters.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Exact marker quantification, not just presence</li>
